      "content": "it's just so exhausting though. staying alive feels like a chore i didn't sign up for. if the universe is just this cold, empty place that doesn't care about us, why is there such a huge pressure to keep surviving? it feels like we're being forced to endure unnecessary suffering for a joke that isn't even funny.",
